Enquire on WhatsApp
</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x500?text=Party+Wear">
<h3>Party Wear WL002</h3>
<a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/918238193632?text=Hi%20Wedding%20Wear%20Studio,%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20Product%20WL002" target="_blank">
Enquire on WhatsApp
</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x500?text=Saree">
<h3>Designer Saree WL003</h3>
<a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/918238193632?text=Hi%20Wedding%20Wear%20Studio,%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20Product%20WL003" target="_blank">
Enquire on WhatsApp
</a>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>
